                    Gather, Sign-in and Fellowship
                </h2> 
                <p>
                    If you tell people that your meeting is going to start at 7:00, tell people to arrive at 6:50, which will give them time to get a seat and sign in so that you can start right on-time.   Have your sign in sheet out and pass it around as people are arriving.
                </p> 
