            </h2>
            <p>
                Again, tonight I am asking each of you to be a part of our congregations Justice  Network to come to our Community Problems Assembly, Rally Assembly, Celebration, our winter congregational meeting and bring 3 others to the Nehemiah Assembly.  I have already told (Clergy/Pastor Name) that I would be a Network Member for our congregation  and I am committing to attend all 4 assemblies and bring 3 people to the Nehemiah Assembly.
            </p>

            <p>
                I would like to ask each of you if you would be willing to do the same.
            </p>
            <p>
                [NOTE for Facilitator:  At this point go around the room and ask each person individually if they will be a network member for your congregation.  Example:  “Bob, would you be willing to be a network member and come to 4 meetings a year and bring 3 people to the Nehemiah Assembly?  Great thank you. Sally would you be willing to…?  Great.  Joan would you be willing to…?  Etc. etc.]
            </p>
        </div>

