            <p>
                I want to thank everyone who came tonight.  I am really excited to be a part of this work and I am glad that you have been and are going to be a part of it too.
                I’d like to give everyone a chance to quickly evaluate the meeting.  If we could just go around the circle and, if you would, just say one word about what you thought about the meeting.  I’ll start, my one word is _________.
            </p>
        </div> 

